sections.History:
===Season 1===
[[Catelyn Stark]] notes a [[knight]] bearing the sigil of House Whent at the [[Crossroads Inn]]. She asks [[Willis Wode|him]] if Lady Whent remains a strong vassal of her father's. When he replies this is so, she recruits him to help her arrest [[Tyrion Lannister]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Cripples, Bastards and Broken Things]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

House Whent lost Harrenhal when it was given to [[Janos Slynt]] for his assistance in betraying [[Eddard Stark]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Baelor]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt; Harrenhal had already fallen under the control of [[House Lannister]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Fire and Blood]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
